Name: Temp Zero
About the game: Pick your weapon, your spell, your music, and you are ready to go. DESTROY EVERYTHING Sword, grenades, teleport? Choose your way to go, and blast your enemies in flow with the music! MUSICAL BULLET HELL Canon, lasers, arrows, explosive shapes and more! Everything strikes to the beat! The higher the tempo, the higher the difficulty, use your dash to get away! GO THROUGH ALL ROOMS You will have to face many rooms full of enemies. Each one with its own layout and bullet hell pattern. BECOME STRONGER Want more weapon damage? More health? More dashes? Pick perks to complete your build! UNLOCK EVERYTHING Get new weapons, new spells, new soundtracks, and unlock trophies you can expose above your head! THE GAME IS TOO EASY? Add spikes, reduce your sight, add some glitching TV filter, face as many challenges as you can! GET THE CROWN Compete with other players in a daily leaderboard with unique rewards! FEATURES Game feel tuned with care. A catchy original soundtrack by the composer of Neon Beats. Many weapons and spells with unique mechanics. Challenges to increase the difficulty. More than 64 trophies to unlock. A leaderboard which resets every day.
